[61.091975, "o", "# Operations\r\n\r\nThe control binary supports `matrix` and `one <scenario>` modes. Matrix mode writes the combined audit under the output directory configured at build time.\r\n\r\nScenario scripts live under `data/cases/` as line-oriented operation lists.\r\n\u001b[?2004hroot@9bc1d408efaf:/app# "]
